{"tid":772162,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［紅磚工程］2018 PolyU Engine新生全攻略","createTime":"2018-08-08T13:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T14:07:25.000Z","uid":136934,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f463b891ad8f6db35e42b11ad19f550222764d02","tid":772162,"uid":136934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>歡迎今年嘅新生加入Poly Engine嘅大家庭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong> </span><br />\n知道每年新生啱啱收到offer，對ocamp、oday或者係前途嘅相關資訊都會十分之迷惘！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我就幫幫手整理一下相關資訊啦！<br />\n<br />\n首先，如果你係屬於以下科目嘅人，你就係屬於工程學院嘅新生：<br />\n<strong>經Jupas入學嘅朋友：</strong><br />\n🔧#JS3064 HD in Electrical Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3076 HD in Electronic &amp; Information Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3117 HD in Industrial &amp; Systems Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3313  Broad Discipline of Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3351 BEng (Hons) in Transportation Systems Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3507 BEng (Hons) in Aviation Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3519 BSc (Hons) in Internet &amp; Multimedia Technologies<br />\n🔧#JS3557 BEng (Hons) Scheme in Product and Industrial Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3571 BSc (Hons) Scheme in Logistics and Enterprise Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3600 BSc (Hons) in Biomedical Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3703 BEng (Hons) in Electronic &amp; Information Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3715 BEng (Hons) in Electrical Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3741 BEng (Hons) Scheme in Mechanical Engineering<br />\n🔧#JS3868 Broad Discipline of Computing<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Non-Jupas入學嘅朋友：</strong><br />\n🔧#61431-SY Broad Discipline of Computing<br />\n🔧#61434 BSc (Hons) in Financial Technology <br />\n🔧#48401 BEng (Hons) in Air Transport Engineering <br />\n🔧#45497 BSc (Hons) in Aviation Operations and Systems<br />\n🔧#47401-SY BSc (Hons) in Biomedical Engineering<br />\n🔧#41470-SY BEng (Hons) in Electrical Engineering<br />\n🔧#42470-SY BEng (Hons) in Electronic &amp; Information Engineering<br />\n🔧#45499-SYE BSc (Hons) in Enterprise Engineering with Management <br />\n🔧#45498-SYI BEng (Hons) in Industrial and Systems Engineering <br />\n🔧#42480 BSc (Hons) in Information Security <br />\n🔧#42477-SY BSc (Hons) in Internet &amp; Multimedia Technologies<br />\n🔧#45499-SYL BSc (Hons) in Logistics Engineering with Management <br />\n🔧#43499-SYM BEng (Hons) Scheme in Mechanical Engineering<br />\n🔧#43499-SYP BEng (Hons) in Product Analysis and Engineering Design <br />\n🔧#45498-SYP BEng (Hons) in Product Engineering with Marketing <br />\n🔧#41481-SY BEng (Hons) in Transportation Systems Engineering"},{"pid":"6d5571020bb9e4c1e12686fcbcf55ed841121f09","tid":772162,"uid":894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"Fm留名"},{"pid":"1fd13679958b9ddb994c2f9049093b75e2c8f5a6","tid":772162,"uid":198460,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:01:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾中O打手要全面進場了嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3300a39e6f0133bcdfb96666fd33173808883c","tid":772162,"uid":65017,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"bd仔留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇tg group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227674a3e1c7d6da0f15859588cbff20e508f0da","tid":772162,"uid":11721,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:44:33.000Z","msg":"JS3313路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6a287f9c7e1a913105aa7765a48e6ea5b2d4ac","tid":772162,"uid":137695,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"毒撚應否玩OCamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550894c4602094f9c3bc334941b2f72bd8865cc3","tid":772162,"uid":137