66df5267507b9d965ec40bdba1fe5101d77aa1","tid":772162,"uid":75868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"認真講<br />\n中O有好多都係冇細O玩既BD仔<br />\n而BD仔好多都係將來既ME EE仔<br />\n所以為識groupmate而玩中O既話唔係呢兩科既人就不了"},{"pid":"34a8a84ca00881efced67aea67ae4ddea0d1d6a0","tid":772162,"uid":65017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7866df5267507b9d965ec40bdba1fe5101d77aa1","tid":772162,"uid":75868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"認真講<br />\n中O有好多都係冇細O玩既BD仔<br />\n而BD仔好多都係將來既ME EE仔<br />\n所以為識groupmate而玩中O既話唔係呢兩科既人就不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"我都有興趣讀呢兩科阿都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我oday睇睇中o先 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd7f3fbb4f99904190b46491bdce96a05b4a53e","tid":772162,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7866df5267507b9d965ec40bdba1fe5101d77aa1","tid":772162,"uid":75868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"認真講<br />\n中O有好多都係冇細O玩既BD仔<br />\n而BD仔好多都係將來既ME EE仔<br />\n所以為識groupmate而玩中O既話唔係呢兩科既人就不了"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"起碼想識左一齊讀yr1嘅fd先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚毒撚一個"},{"pid":"56b5eaec9bcd79f96a27401eda8401fa79e6f8bb","tid":772162,"uid":136934,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:20:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1. ODay資訊</strong></span></span><br />\n一年一度嘅ODay係一個為各位Freshman帶嚟好多有用信息嘅一個活動，例如<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>學校設施嘅資料</strong></span>呀、你<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>嚟緊會讀嗰科嘅內容</strong></span>、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>前景</strong></span>等等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nODay入面嘅攤位係由一班讀Engine嘅師兄師姐Hold嘅！對於未來嘅學年有咩疑難，或者有興趣嘅記得到時問班親切嘅哥哥姐姐啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，如果想係學期開始前識到一班同你一齊上堂、一齊食飯、一齊打機、放假一齊去玩嘅朋友，咁就唔好錯過會係ODay開放報名嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>OCamp</strong></span>啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係2018ODay嘅時間，記得留意啦！<br />\n日期：<strong>八月十二至八月十三日</strong><br />\n時間：<strong>上午十時正到下午六時正</strong><br />\n地點：<strong>邵逸夫樓體育館</strong><br />\n<br />\n當日記得帶以下嘅物品啦！<br />\n1. <strong>錢</strong>（報ocamp之用）- 1個ocamp約$200-500, 視乎返唔同嘅Ocamp，至於有咩OCamp之後講<br />\n2. <strong>身份證</strong> <br />\n3. <strong>eAdmission 嘅Notice of offer Hard Copy</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. <strong>SU Fee比咗錢嘅Finance Office網上收據 或者 自己SU Fee debit note hard copy+唔同比錢方法收據(入數紙又或者網上過數等)</strong><br />\n5. <strong>迎新營活動家長/監護人同意書</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (未滿十八歲嘅freshman要填完交去booth）<br />\n<br />\n另外都可以參考返呢個post，資料都幾齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/768766/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/768766/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"76ab0d7c62309f1a37375ebb8bb0dac7bf843cd3","tid":772162,"uid":136934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2. OCamp資訊</strong></span></span><br />\n相信大家都聽過咩係OCamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOCamp係各個society搞比Freshman嘅迎新營，比fm bb認識下嚟緊嘅同學同新朋友，同時比大家窺探下未來嘅大學生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講起OCamp大家一定聽過好多人講中O細O，到底咩係中O同細O、佢地有咩分別？唔洗急，且聽我娓娓道來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中O</span></strong></span>其實就係由<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">學院會</span></span></strong>搞嘅OCamp，對象係你所就讀嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">學院嘅同學</span></span></strong>，即係除咗可以識同你同科嘅朋友之外，仲可以識埋一樣係讀Engine嘅其他同學，而year1會有好多科都一齊讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>細O</strong></span></span>，即係由<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學科會或學系會</span></span></strong>舉辦嘅OCamp，對象僅為<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">讀該學科嘅同學</span></span></strong>，相對而言對象比較狹窄，但係佢地有好大可能成為你日後上堂嘅同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於今年嘅工程學院嘅OCamps就會喺ODay嘅攤位開放報名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中O攤位開放時間</span></span></strong> ： <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">八月十二日上午十時正至下午六時正</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大部分細O攤位開放時間</span></span></strong> ： <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">八月十二日至十三日上午十時正至下午六時正</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中O同細O嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">收費由150-400</span></strong></span>不等，想兩個都報齊嘅就記得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">帶多啲錢啦！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e6d785acc5114e1565409b6852b458a7911e54","tid":772162,"uid":136934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3300a39e6f0133bcdfb96666fd33173808883c","tid":772162,"uid":65017,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"bd仔留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇tg group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JylnZw30NGGVpXvJlLhe5A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJylnZw30NGGVpXvJlLhe5A&d=O%2B%2FmjTQdNMYEhUtediYwEjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3c2ce73d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JylnZw30NGGVpXvJlLhe5A</a><br />\n隔離Post有呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbfcb07aeeb8f28643b8da78ee6cedd05f8025d","tid":772162,"uid":75868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6dd7f3fbb4f99904190b46491bdce96a05b4a53e","tid":772162,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7866df5267507b9d965ec40bdba1fe5101d77aa1","tid":772162,"uid":75868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"認真講<br />\n中O有好多都係冇細O玩既BD仔<br />\n而BD仔好多都係將來既ME EE仔<br />\n所以為識groupmate而玩中O既話唔係呢兩科既人就不了"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"起碼想識左一齊讀yr1嘅fd先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚毒撚一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:33:11.000Z","msg":"雖然話就話科科engine yr1都係讀差唔多一樣既科<br />\n但因為太多engine仔所以其實都係會分左唔同班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如你地黎緊sem1會讀果科AMA1110, BD同ME一班, 大電同細電一班等等<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得中O最多BD同ME, 其次係大電細電AE<br />\nBME同ISE呢D少到唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63b8adbbc34604add950d5343f19ff78dbd8038","tid":772162,"uid":65017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd7f3fbb4f99904190b46491bdce96a05b4a53e","tid":772162,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7866df5267507b9d965ec40bdba1fe5101d77aa1","tid":772162,"uid":75868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"認真講<br />\n中O有好多都係冇細O玩既BD仔<br />\n而BD仔好多都係將來既ME EE仔<br />\n所以為識groupmate而玩中O既話唔係呢兩科既人就不了"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"起碼想識左一齊讀yr1嘅fd先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.g